FBIS4-59492 "drnes094dd_94018" FBIS-NES-94-094 Daily Report 15 May 1994 Palestinian Affairs Hamas Reportedly To Cooperate With PLO Police Hamas Reportedly To Cooperate With PLO Police LD1505202594 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network in Persian 1930 GMT 15 May 94 LD1505202594 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network Persian BFN [Text] A spokesman for Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement], while pledging to continue the struggle against the occupiers of al-Quds [Jerusalem], announced: The combatants of Palestine's Islamic Resistance Movement will cooperate with the Palestine police in the Gaza and Jericho regions for as long as the laws and regulations of this police correspond with the idea ruling over this Movement.
